{"type": "article", "id": 17657, "title": "Dior 进军电子商务，以及，有个设计师做的冰山蜡烛还不错 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2015-11-17T09:56:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 634, "name": "王大仁"}, {"id": 2034, "name": "Dior"}, {"id": 1330, "name": "ASOS"}, {"id": 1060, "name": "H&M"}, {"id": 681, "name": "Ralph Lauren"}, {"id": 18846, "name": "Urban Outfitter"}, {"id": 15629, "name": "the Weekend"}, {"id": 18847, "name": "Just Don"}, {"id": 18848, "name": "What?Watch"}, {"id": 17749, "name": "yeezy"}, {"id": 15116, "name": "Y-3"}, {"id": 3592, "name": "The North Face"}, {"id": 8634, "name": "Supreme"}, {"id": 18849, "name": "Ellis Brooklyn"}, {"id": 129, "name": "Kate Moss"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 75588, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 78, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606142103Gb8uXvnRIQk6Z021.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h3>\r\n\t一些重要的新闻：\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"><strong><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Dior-enters-e-commerce-arena-with-Bergdorf-pop-up,596501.html#.Vkpbw4RVfBI\" target=\"_blank\">Dior 进军电子商务</a>｜</strong>周日 Christian Dior 宣布将在著名奢侈品百货店 Bergdorf Goodman 的官网上开启“在线快闪店”，出售假日鞋履系列，包含 14 种风格的鞋子，价格在 $830 至 $1100，售卖将进行到 12 月31日。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"><strong><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/H-M-October-sales-12-percent-just-below-expectations,596383.html#.VkpdooRVfBI\" target=\"_blank\">H&amp;M 十月销售涨 12% 略低于预期</a>｜</strong>世界第二的时尚连锁品牌 H&amp;M（Hennes &amp; Mauritz）据报道 10 月的销售额与去年同期相比上涨了 12%，与预期的 13% 相比稍低。截至去年 10月 31 世界拥有 3437 家门店，今年为 3807 家。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Ralph-Lauren-opens-first-Polo-store-in-Rome,596192.html\" target=\"_blank\">Polo Ralph Lauren 开意大利首家门店</a>｜</strong>Polo Ralph Lauren 日前宣布将在罗马 Via del Corso 和 Via Frattina 拐角处一栋古建筑中开出品牌在意大利的第一家门店。5000 平方英尺、两层的面积，用于售卖男装、鞋履、配饰及皮制品。据悉，公司将继续在世界尤其是欧洲地区的扩张。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong><a href=\"http://www.racked.com/2015/11/16/9743362/urban-outfitters-italian-restaurant-group-stock\" target=\"_blank\">Urban Outfitter 投资了餐饮业</a>｜</strong>Urban Outfitter 看来不止想做购物店，最近刚刚收购了一家意式餐饮集团。后者名为 Vetri 餐饮家族集团，来自费城，拥有意大利披萨连锁店。尽管 UO 已经在自己门店内开始售卖一些食物，此次收购会将使 Vetri 来专注负责餐饮。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t一些值得一看的：\r\n</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<span>王大仁和 the weeknd 合作发布胶囊系列 <span style=\"text-align:start;\">“WANGXO”</span>，</span>系列包括 T 恤，帽衫，头巾，鞋子等单品，上面都有 XO 字样。美国时间明天可以在王大仁官网上购买。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142042LJVbcm6N3OBZqTgA.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.49925037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142043xUG0mdO42QNLqnTz.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.25166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142044IhUyvBOlMsQewq1f.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.34666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142044s1RCVuhJt5n2FiX3.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66611018\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\tASOS 婚纱更多 Look 全曝光，<a href=\"http://www.whowhatwear.com/asos-bridal-collection-launch-spring-2016\" target=\"_blank\">明年 4 月</a>开始售卖<span style=\"text-align:left;\">，价格大约在 380 美元左右。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:left;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060614204457jNRToe0LYy9xdb.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.27521793\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061420459n41zrUhN3Buk5aY.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.17836594\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061420451RVyCfKor0wH3MPE.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.17836594\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061420465afj0E2Jm1QZpder.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.17836594\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142046NzMquywQImjhR75s.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.17836594\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142046fw7lkXDRQUB5hWeu.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.17836594\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142047VRufay5TO4pnW3HQ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.17836594\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142047rwFDqsxHJmTBzlKX.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.17836594\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142048qdugXo3NZUrQpPCt.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.17836594\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142048reZDR0OUEBFj9Ptx.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.17836594\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142049M0Svm7ObIfD1sGZQ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.17836594\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span>乌克兰设计师 Konstantin Kofta 一向以其几何轮廓和来自大自然的设计灵感所闻名。这次 2016 春夏系列包包「Arxi」，参照 16 世纪的巴洛克式建筑的风格，灵感来源于那些自然雕塑和戏剧性的曲线，将圣殿和古典的寺庙上的图案和轮廓，融入到新包的设计中，并给人以视觉上的错觉。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142049ZFMHUdJt7PN38bzB.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142049cTWjM09tV7wFguPJ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142050s6ION8x7gSAjChYL.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142050E9cS0I8Wg1oaRJHN.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061420518zjpnNGyf05WuarL.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061420515DULSng462Ww9YVr.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142052m2wPNluqjJ7IAeD9.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>Just Don 推出奢侈运动系列，表皮使用的是蟒蛇皮，价格在 $1500 到 $2400 左右，在<span></span><a href=\"http://justdon.com/collections/accessories\" target=\"_blank\">这里</a><span></span>可以买到。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142052HxLaKmge8hZFjGBJ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144755VgvyQu2XF34jdYfz.jpg\" width=\"1023\" height=\"682\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142053NvgBXDHwYjbelitT.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t布鲁克林设计师品牌What?Watch推出一个号称停止时间的腕表，虽然并非真的停止时间，但在腕表的侧面有一个红色按钮具有记录时刻功能，每个月最多可以保存 5 次，要<a href=\"http://itunes.apple.com/us/app/what-now/id952670682?mt=8&amp;ign-mpt=uo%3D4\" target=\"_blank\">结合 APP 使用</a>。售价 299 美元，链接在<a href=\"http://www.whatwatch.com/\" target=\"_blank\">这里</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142053vqsQbfFprgZHOnUR.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061420548lyaNphKCBw2mTiA.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142054Qw9zncZsKlCbFJBE.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142055yOE1okbqMCsTclBe.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142055rGfQczabpHPJY3i2.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t根据 GQ 消息，YEEZY 750 黑色版将在 12 月 5 日推出。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142056ZcNr4fOtECQRqLk6.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66796875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\tSupreme 与 The North Face 2015 秋冬联名系列的完整单品图片和定价释出。该系列包括有 Nuptse Jacket、Mountain Pullover、Base Camp Crimp Backpack、Base Camp Travel Canister 与 Winter Runners Gloves 等 5 件单品，均以「By Any Means Necessary.」的白色标语贯穿。系列将于 11 月 19 日开始在 Supreme 纽约、洛杉矶和伦敦门店与线上店铺发售。美元定价请参考以下：Nupste Jacket : $368Mountain Pullover : $298Base Camp Crimp Backpack : $148Base Camp Travel Canister : $32Winter Runners Gloves : $58。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061420568LrKc0ztSXWRa2Dq.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142057xcWNCabHA5UXzu36.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142058XngHc7FQS2tT6d51.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142058QnBGhsD6ouYH0PdE.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142059zajIUoAiJxuOrfmK.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142059eLQtDs7qVOubX3An.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142100x12nPq9MCJiOSeuN.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t瑞士设计师 Brynjar Siguroarson 推出冰山蜡烛系列，提供五种尺寸，一套的价格为 59 美元，戳<a href=\"http://www.gnr8.biz/glacier-project-candles.html\" target=\"_blank\">这里</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142100NB2in3bAoy7u0XYz.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.59960938\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061421010jl2LuIV9R1pUdhw.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.7496136\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>纽约时报记者 Bee Shapiro 创建的一个香氛品牌，叫做 <a href=\"http://www.ellisbrooklyn.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Ellis Brooklyn</a>，记者如何做品牌，或许你会感兴趣。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142101WBEgtTSpGYLqNKai.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142101Tp63zv75QEPRnSGw.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142102BekcdoDJMX2y7uER.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.4037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>Y-3 2016 春夏鞋类单品图释放，系列将在明年 3 月开售。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142102B5UEKJ9cRa0qmZyC.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.93518519\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h4 style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n\t一些有意思的说法：\r\n</h4>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t在这个明星和红人们玩转社交媒体的时代，名模 Kate Moss 的 Instagram 账号却并不设置成公开，而只供好友follow。她表明账号只用来纪录自己的生活和\"spying\" 功能——看看别人的状态以及大伙儿正在谈论什么，希望自己不要太落后潮流。她并不在乎别人晚餐吃什么和天气如何，也说自己与社交媒体关系一般，还不擅长自拍。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}